desc_long							评测						“sublime focus on the story and productions coupled with psychedelic and monochromatic art that is a fresh addition to the genre”TechARX“Experimental, trippy, runner game. Actually way better than it sounds.”Jim Sterling“Aesthetically gorgeous, (...) a bit too brutal. Definitely worth a look though.”Pocket Gamer												关于这款游戏							The year is 1994 and it is the future.NO THING is a minimalistic surreal action game set in a totalitarian regime of future.Tells the story of an office clerk who is sent with an important message to the Queen of Ice.NO THING Features: radical gameplay migraine inducing weird storyline retro surrealistic full 3D graphic full voiceover and speech synthesis chiptune sounds original cold wave music simple controls easy to play, very hard to master platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux the year is 1994 and it is the future 						
